        <docTitle>Resolution adopted by the General Assembly on 15 March 2022</docTitle>
      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docProponent refersTo="#noMainCommittee">[without reference to a Main Committee (<inline name="originating document">A/76/L.41 and A/76/L.41/Add.1</inline>)]</docProponent>
